Package: ircor
Title: Correlation Coefficients for Information Retrieval
Version: 0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Julián", "Urbano", email = "urbano.julian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Mónica", "Marrero", email = "marrero.monica@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: Provides implementation of various correlation coefficients of common use in
  Information Retrieval, such as Kendall and AP correlation coefficients, with and without ties.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
